<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>Plain <rs type="material" key="marmor">white marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">base</rs>, weathered (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.42</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.66</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.39</measure>), with holes in the top for attachment of a capital.</p>
</div>

<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs>  on the lower fascia (<measure dim="width" type="length" unit="metre">0.51</measure> × <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.10</measure>). The main text containing the decision must have been inscribed on a base below.</p>
</div>

<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Description of Letters</head>
<p><measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.025-0.03</measure>; circle for stop.</p>
</div>

<div type="description" n="date">
 <head>Date</head>

<p>     Probably <date exact="none" notAfter="0100" notBefore="0001" cert="low">first century A.D.</date> (<rs type="criteria">lettering</rs>).</p></div>

