<div type="translation">
<head>Translation</head>
<p>The Council and the People and the Young Men honoured Panphilos Krokion son of Artemon who lived honourably and with due order. Artemon Bacchios son of Artemon <supplied reason="subaudible">set up</supplied> Krokion his brother.</p></div>

